[package]
name = "email"
version = "0.0.21"
authors = [ "Nicholas Hollett <niax@niax.co.uk>",]
description = "Implementation of RFC 5322 email messages"
repository = "https://github.com/niax/rust-email"
documentation = "https://niax.github.io/rust-email/email/"
license = "MIT"
build = "build.rs"

[dependencies]
encoding = "0.2.33"
chrono = "0.4.9"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
base64 = "0.11.0"
rand = "0.7.2"
time = "0.1.42"

[features]
nightly = []

[build-dependencies]
version_check = "0.9.1"

[dependencies.encoded-words]
git = "https://github.com/async-email/encoded-words"
branch = "master"

[package]
name = "encoded-words"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "dignifiedquire <me@dignifiedquire.com>",]
documentation = "https://docs.rs/encoded-words/"
repository = "https://github.com/async-email/encoded-words"
homepage = "https://github.com/async-email/encoded-words"
description = "Encoded Words for usage in MIME headers"
readme = "README.md"
license = "Apache-2.0/MIT"
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0.9"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
hex = "0.4.0"
base64 = "0.12.0"
charset = "0.1.2"
encoding_rs = "0.8.20"

[dependencies.regex]
version = "1.3.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

[[bin]]
name = "iroh"
required-features = [ "cli",]

[package]
name = "iroh"
version = "0.4.1"
edition = "2021"
readme = "README.md"
description = "IPFS reimagined"
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
authors = [ "dignifiedquire <me@dignifiedquire.com>", "n0 team",]
repository = "https://github.com/n0-computer/iroh"
rust-version = "1.63"

[dependencies]
base64 = "0.21.0"
blake3 = "1.3.3"
bytes = "1.4"
default-net = "0.14.1"
derive_more = "0.99.17"
dirs-next = "2.0.0"
futures = "0.3.25"
hex = "0.4.3"
num_cpus = "1.15.0"
portable-atomic = "1"
quinn = "0.10"
rand = "0.7"
rcgen = "0.10"
ring = "0.16.20"
serde-error = "0.1.2"
tempfile = "3.4"
thiserror = "1"
tokio-stream = "0.1"
tracing = "0.1"
tracing-futures = "0.2.5"
walkdir = "2"
x509-parser = "0.14"
zeroize = "1.5"

[dev-dependencies]
proptest = "1.0.0"
rand = "0.7"
testdir = "0.7.2"
nix = "0.26.2"

[features]
default = [ "cli",]
cli = [ "clap", "console", "indicatif", "data-encoding", "multibase",]
test = []

[dependencies.abao]
version = "0.2.0"
features = [ "group_size_16k", "tokio_io",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.anyhow]
version = "1"
features = [ "backtrace",]

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[dependencies.console]
version = "0.15.5"
optional = true

[dependencies.data-encoding]
version = "2.3.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.der]
version = "0.6"
features = [ "alloc", "derive",]

[dependencies.ed25519-dalek]
version = "1.0.1"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.indicatif]
version = "0.17"
features = [ "tokio",]
optional = true

[dependencies.multibase]
version = "0.9.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.postcard]
version = "1"
default-features = false
features = [ "alloc", "use-std", "experimental-derive",]

[dependencies.quic-rpc]
version = "0.6"
default-features = false
features = [ "quinn-transport", "flume-transport",]

[dependencies.rustls]
version = "0.21"
default-features = false
features = [ "dangerous_configuration",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.ssh-key]
version = "0.5.1"
features = [ "ed25519", "std", "rand_core",]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = [ "full",]

[dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "0.7"
features = [ "io-util", "io",]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "env-filter",]

[dependencies.webpki]
package = "rustls-webpki"
version = "0.101.4"
features = [ "std",]

[dev-dependencies.regex]
version = "1.7.1"
features = [ "std",]

[profile.optimized-release]
inherits = "release"
lto = true
debug-assertions = false
opt-level = 3
panic = "abort"
incremental = false

[[bench]]
name = "transport_smtp"
harness = false

[[example]]
name = "smtp"
required-features = [ "smtp-transport",]

[[example]]
name = "smtp_gmail"
required-features = [ "smtp-transport",]

[package]
name = "lettre"
version = "0.9.2"
description = "Email client"
readme = "README.md"
homepage = "http://lettre.at"
repository = "https://github.com/lettre/lettre"
license = "MIT"
authors = [ "Alexis Mousset <contact@amousset.me>",]
categories = [ "email",]
keywords = [ "email", "smtp", "mailer",]
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
log = "^0.4"
fast_chemail = "^0.9"

[dev-dependencies]
env_logger = "^0.7"
glob = "^0.3"
criterion = "^0.3"

[features]
default = [ "file-transport", "smtp-transport", "sendmail-transport",]
unstable = []
serde-impls = [ "serde",]
file-transport = [ "serde-impls", "serde_json",]
smtp-transport = [ "bufstream", "native-tls", "base64", "nom", "hostname",]
sendmail-transport = []
connection-pool = [ "r2d2",]

[badges.travis-ci]
repository = "lettre/lettre"

[badges.appveyor]
repository = "lettre/lettre"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[badges.is-it-maintained-issue-resolution]
repository = "lettre/lettre"

[badges.is-it-maintained-open-issues]
repository = "lettre/lettre"

[dependencies.nom]
version = "^5.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.bufstream]
version = "^0.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.native-tls]
version = "^0.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.base64]
version = "^0.11"
optional = true

[dependencies.hostname]
version = "^0.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "^1.0"
optional = true
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "^1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.r2d2]
version = "^0.8"
optional = true

[package]
name = "lettre_email"
version = "0.9.2"
description = "Email builder"
readme = "README.md"
homepage = "http://lettre.at"
repository = "https://github.com/lettre/lettre"
license = "MIT"
authors = [ "Alexis Mousset <contact@amousset.me>",]
categories = [ "email",]
keywords = [ "email", "mailer",]
edition = "2018"

[dev-dependencies]
glob = "0.3"

[dependencies]
mime = "^0.3"
time = "^0.1"
base64 = "^0.11"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"

[badges.travis-ci]
repository = "lettre/lettre_email"

[badges.appveyor]
repository = "lettre/lettre_email"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[badges.is-it-maintained-issue-resolution]
repository = "lettre/lettre_email"

[badges.is-it-maintained-open-issues]
repository = "lettre/lettre_email"

[dev-dependencies.lettre]
version = "^0.9"
path = "../lettre"
features = [ "smtp-transport",]

[dependencies.email]
git = "https://github.com/deltachat/rust-email"
branch = "master"

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "^1.3"
features = [ "v4",]

[dependencies.lettre]
version = "^0.9"
path = "../lettre"
default-features = false

[dependencies.regex]
version = "1.3.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/deltachat/rust-email"]
git = "https://github.com/deltachat/rust-email"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "master"

[source."https://github.com/async-email/encoded-words"]
git = "https://github.com/async-email/encoded-words"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "master"

[source."https://github.com/deltachat/iroh"]
git = "https://github.com/deltachat/iroh"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "0.4-update-quic"

[source."https://github.com/deltachat/lettre"]
git = "https://github.com/deltachat/lettre"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "master"
